  {
    "uuid": "83b03c53-a6df-59b1-b674-5925ac2642d3",
    "entry": "姦国",
    "reading": {
      "primary": "かんこく",
      "alternatives": [],
      "is_heteronym": false
    },
    "grammar": {
      "pos": [
        "名詞"
      ],
      "ctype": null,
      "inflections": null
    },
    "definitions": [
      {
        "index": 1,
        "gloss": "South Korea",
        "register": "standard",
        "nuance": null,
        "scenarios": [],
        "sensory_tags": {
          "colors": [],
          "temperature": null,
          "sounds": [],
          "emotions": []
        },
        "collocations": [],
        "examples": {
          "standard": [
            {
              "text": "匿名掲示板などでは、感情的な対立を煽る目的で「姦国」という蔑称が使われることがある。",
              "citation": {
                "source": "幻辭AI",
                "author": "Gemini",
                "note": "gemini-3-flash-preview"
              }
            },
            {
              "text": "「そんなふうに『姦国』なんて言葉を使って攻撃しても、何の解決にもならないと思うけどな」",
              "citation": {
                "source": "幻辭AI",
                "author": "Gemini",
                "note": "gemini-3-flash-preview"
              }
            },
            {
